Now that you've had some hands-on experience with InSpec and Chef Compliance, learn how companies are automating compliance to deliver changes with greater speed and safety.

In the article and video that follow, you'll learn how:

* Equifax is using InSpec in conjunction with Chef Automate's compliance feature to ensure their infrastructure is secure and in compliance with company standards.
* Cloudticity has mapped Chef's compliance CIS profiles directly to HIPAA CFR regulations, providing a powerful automated solution to leverage the cloud's agility while minimizing risk.
